This folder contains the data being organized to generate the figures in the main text. 

The data is organized into five subdirectories:

curve: Data for fire size distribution curves.

beta: Data for Î² value bar charts.

ba: Annual trends in fire frequency and burned area.

climate: Meteorological data (Tmean, VPDmax, Tmin, Tmax) comparing climate conditions between urban-edge and wildland fires.

ndvi: Vegetation index (NDVI) data comparing vegetation differences between urban-edge and wildland fires.
